social-intentions-and-promotes-dependence</guid></item><item><title>创新以帮助长期病人蓬勃发展</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2025/10/innovations-to-help-chronically-ill-people-thrive</link><description>斯坦福医学专家正在开发创新的方法来预防，诊断和治疗慢性疾病，以便人们可以过上更健康的生活。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/innovations-to-help-chronically-ill-people-thrive.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Oct 2025 12:09:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2025/10/innovations-to-help-chronically-ill-people-thrive</guid></item></channel></rss>